{"tid":2448277,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔鐘意「致敬」呢個term","createTime":"2021-03-15T22:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T00:27:46.000Z","uid":364453,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"736e40b461d96fe3918fff6fe15935cb0fb595ae","tid":2448277,"uid":364453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T22:10:26.000Z","msg":"唔係好清楚佢個源頭係咪匪語<br />\n<br />\n但係以前好似冇聽過呢個term<br />\n可能係我唔識嘢<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他講法可以代替佢<br />\n感覺香港話好似冇呢個概念<br />\n<br />\n香港話似係直接講條片點reference啲舊嘅嘢<br />\n大概好似：<br />\n<br />\n「銀魂呢個op惡搞緊k-on同其他動漫」<br />\n「試當真新年條片玩緊supa hot fire meme」<br />\n陳述啲搞笑嘅referencing可以咁講<br />\n<br />\n「試當真呢條片參考/重現咗落水狗嘅橋段」<br />\n「RMBJ 唱嗰首迷途羔羊中間插咗段縱貫線首亡命之徒嘅旋律」<br />\n陳述認真啲嘅referencing似乎可以咁講<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你話返比我知「致敬」其實係好正統好大路嘅香港話我會嘗試接受返佢<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 請指教，促進下香港話發展<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5fiDeC4zBLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5fiDeC4zBLM&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=3aaa389b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5fiDeC4zBLM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fma8xxecY38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffma8xxecY38&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=7476ba6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fma8xxecY38</a>"},{"pid":"835b3c984c45d3af6c9af19534090bae7e040aa6","tid":2448277,"uid":16414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T22:16:43.000Z","msg":"應該係中國以外用先<br />\n尤其係創作方面嘅致敬<br />\n中國未有呢個概念之前香港已經有<br />\n<br />\n不過因為近年中國賣仿製品<br />\n如果叫&quot;A貨&quot;&quot;高仿&quot;就上唔到佢地嘅購物網<br />\n所以最近都叫&quot;致敬&quot;&quot;復刻&quot;<br />\n<br />\n家下假Rolex 係叫&quot;100%復刻&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53833c850337efcf3e607aad6c8c2b33305fa43","tid":2448277,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T22:18:02.000Z","msg":"只能夠講佢唔係中國製嘅新式中文lo<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯的話讀書時見文言文有出現過<br />\n<br />\